arts.ttl: A new test of maturity for Milan awaits against Pisa
arts.sum: The win against Fiorentina marked an important milestone in what could become Milan’s path from here on. A win of heart, anger, and unity. A win that brought the Rossoneri back to the top of the table alone, 743 days after the last time, and that now, perhaps for the first time in a while, […]
